     // Also:
     if (Object.hasOwn(customPaths, seriesSlug)) continue;
     const isAutoSeriesPath = getSeriesAutoPaths() && !Object.hasOwn(customPaths, prefix) && getSeriesData(prefix) !== null;
     ```

   - **`src/app/[slug]/page/[page]/page.tsx`**
     - Added `getAllSeries`, `getSeriesAutoPaths` to imports
     - `generateStaticParams`: added autoPaths paginated series params
     - `generateMetadata` and `PrefixPageRoute`: extended `matchedSeriesSlug` to detect autoPaths series
     - Changed `in customPaths` → `Object.hasOwn(customPaths, ...)` in 3 places
     ```typescript
