   - Run `bun run test:unit` to verify all tests pass after the fixes
   - Commit the complete set of changes (`Object.hasOwn` fixes + new tests)

8. Current Work:
   The assistant was in the middle of fixing 6 failing unit tests in `tests/unit/static-params.test.ts` after adding new tests for CodeRabbit's review feedback. The last edit rewrote the `autoPaths enabled` describe block:

